ke":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:35:08.000Z","msg":"肝鬱氣滯，肝鬱結，長年累月都驚一d嘢，擔心一d嘢，緊張一d嘢，甚至長期就黎遲到追巴士咁，個人長期急趕都會，女人比較多。 如果冇乜波或男人，好明顯睇倒係乳頭垂直向下果d位痛。可以痛到呼吸都不能快，手都郁唔倒咁，提起腳行路都會痛，甚至痛到落小腹，忍一陣過咗就冇嘢。  有中藥沖劑食，最好就自己解決情緒問題，春夏天比較多出現。"},{"pid":"1b36880f60db546995430d06c78900a44dd4b9b1","tid":697162,"uid":159021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:40:44.000Z","msg":"如果痛同埋覺得呼吸有困難 胸口翳焗 可能係爆肺 不過巴打先大d機會會爆"},{"pid":"fa4f870bfef548465d72177acbaf3a394a685374","tid":697162,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ce314cb686f36ea48f4e94fab27bc40107b0acc","tid":697162,"uid":56018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"001752719915779ff6529a6cde409ff86c364d31","tid":697162,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f349b0111d01e7917722139c00c3638a4a9ed50","tid":697162,"uid":56018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T18:03:30.000Z","msg":"最好都係去照下啦<br />\n輕嘅話可能就咁肋骨附近發炎<br />\n嚴重嘅話可能個心/肺有事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T18:17:20.000Z","msg":"我左面肋骨兩星期前開始痛<br />\n唔通係肋骨發炎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T18:22:24.000Z","msg":"撳落去痛唔痛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:55:59.000Z","msg":"撳落去會小痛，伸懶腰會痛，<br />\n其餘時間就唔痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會係咩事？"},{"pid":"8e071fe39727243421d09d7f7263e60afbc44318","tid":697162,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T02:01:28.000Z","msg":"心電圖睇到好少嘢，一係照心臟超聲波睇下心肌有冇異常，一係做埋血管造影睇下有冇塞"},{"pid":"ebb3fd0f3788b392a5b356112d153e7bb5fd5fc8","tid":697162,"uid":6640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T02:18:48.000Z","msg":"我係右邊"},{"pid":"8a82ac43af0d6cf5c6644f79376306ade18d785a","tid":697162,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"